Package: autonomics
Type: Package
Title: Generifying and intuifying cross-platform omics analysis
Version: 1.11.6
Authors@R: c(person("Aditya",   "Bhagwat",   email = "aditya.bhagwat@uni-marburg.de",    role = c("aut", "cre")), 
